<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmed - uVision</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .payment-info {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #4caf50;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .confirmation-code {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #2196f3;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1976d2;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üéâ Booking Confirmed!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for choosing uVision</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= clientName %>,</h2>
        <p>Great news! Your booking has been confirmed and your upfront payment has been successfully processed.</p>
        
        <div class="booking-details">
            <h3>üìã Booking Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Booking Number:</strong> <%= bookingNumber %></p>
            <p><strong>Professional:</strong> <%= professionalName %></p>
            <p><strong>Service:</strong> <%= serviceName %></p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= eventDate %></p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= eventTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= location %></p>
            <% if (specialRequests) { %>
            <p><strong>Special Requests:</strong> <%= specialRequests %></p>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="payment-info">
            <h3>üí≥ Payment Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Total Booking Amount:</strong> ‚Ç¨<%= totalAmount %></p>
            <p><strong>Upfront Payment (30%):</strong> ‚Ç¨<%= upfrontAmount %> ‚úÖ <em>Paid</em></p>
            <p><strong>Remaining Amount (70%):</strong> ‚Ç¨<%= remainingAmount %> <em>Due after service completion</em></p>
            <p><strong>Platform Fee:</strong> ‚Ç¨<%= platformFee %> (10% of total)</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="confirmation-code">
            <h3>üîê Your Confirmation Code</h3>
            <p>Use this code to complete final payment after service completion:</p>
            <div class="code"><%= confirmationCode %></div>
            <p><small>Keep this code safe - you'll need it to complete the final 70% payment</small></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>üìå What's Next?</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Professional Contact:</strong> <%= professionalName %> will contact you soon to confirm details</li>
                <li><strong>Attend Session:</strong> Be present at the scheduled date and time</li>
                <li><strong>Service Completion:</strong> After the service is completed, use your confirmation code</li>
                <li><strong>Final Payment:</strong> Complete the remaining 70% payment using the confirmation code above</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes to your booking, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/bookings" class="button">View My Bookings</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>uVision</strong> - Connecting You with Creative Professionals</p>
        <p>üìß support@uvision.com | üìû +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
        <p><small>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this email address.</small></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
